{
  "stem": "23278.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the stores with they-- where Jewish had to have a yellow star in the window.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were advised not to shop there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to my great surprise, practically every store in Dijon was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody thought of it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, when you saw stockings, underwear, perfume, sweaters, shoes, jewelry, beauty products, Helen, Helena Rubinstein, the store there-- all that was yellow star.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Don't go there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My friends who were not Jewish didn't go there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And beside, those poor people didn't have very much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, the little they had was already taken by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never thought of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember a girl called Guggenheim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We thought it was strange, but Guggenheim pronounced in the French way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we never thought of [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Suzanne ?] Guggenheim being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, it never crossed our mind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We never thought in those terms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But all of a sudden, that appeared.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then people had to wear the yellow stars.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my-- my friend-- I wouldn't say school friends-- my schoolmates started to leave the school, the high school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we have a Bloch, Guggenheim, Frank, Oppenheimer, Jacob, Marx.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, all these kids left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why did they leave?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is because the principal asked them one-by-one to come to her office and spoke to them one-by-one telling them it was dangerous.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That if they wanted to stay in Dijon, that was not a good idea.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But if they did, she would manage to have teachers go into the house, continue the teaching.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But if the parents were wise, they should leave.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rita left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My friend Rita left the school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I have to say for our school teachers, they were extremely helpful.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
